Arabic B2B Marketing Manager
BAC Middle East
Dubai Media City, UAE
Posted on: 6 May 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
AED18000 Total Salary Including Housing
On behalf of our client a global PR brand we are looking to recruit an Arabic B2B Marketing Manager. Reporting to the Country Manager-MENA you will be responsible for the creation, execution and management of B2B campaigns in a year round programme of marketing initiatives and PR positioning to support the Commercial Sales Team in order for them to reach their financial targets, implementation of B2B marketing strategies, forge strong relationships with leading B2B agencies, experts and partners, manage and update the Arabic section of company website and act as the main point of contact between ME office and UK head office.
REQUIREMENTS
The successful candidate must be a resident of the UAE, be fluent in all areas of Arabic, have a minimum of 2 years marketing and PR experience from an agency in the UAE, have excellent interpersonal and communication skills, experience with social media in a professional capacity and be able to work independently and proactively.
ABOUT THE COMPANY
BAC Middle East - the longest established professional recruitment consultancy in the UAE. Established in 1979, we have been at the forefront of the region's recruitment industry for 30 years and were the first firm of our type in the world to achieve ISO9001 certification: a reflection of our constant emphasis on quality and customer satisfaction.
With our well-developed infrastructure and staff strength, we are able to assist you with recruitment needs ranging from junior professionals through to middle and senior management, whatever your industry sector.
BAC's proven regional experience and resources can help ensure that you recruit the best available candidates and enjoy the many advantages of a managed recruitment process.
